{"tid":1604422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好鳩屌唔罷工啦...","createTime":"2019-09-30T03:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T05:43:36.000Z","uid":277060,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"32a81de3fb440894fa4c969d5f1992cac5a34dc7","tid":1604422,"uid":277060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:08:19.000Z","msg":"鳩屌有乜用?? <br />\n<br />\n我唔係話罷工無用，問題係未到時候就係未到時候...<br />\n搵份工黎賭，有大有細Ｏ既唔係話鍾意玩就玩...<br />\n你一味鳩叫.. 叫唔到就屌... <br />\n咁你地遲早屌走和理非...<br />\n<br />\n真心... 你地 D 野真係唔使咁密...<br />\n而且做事講時機...<br />\n九二九同十一 take 晒 attention<br />\n九三零仲攝個三罷..<br />\n邊鬼個得閒理你...<br />\n<br />\n一講 D 要全世界一齊做野O既事..<br />\n係真係要時間文宣... 同埋凝聚力..<br />\n唔易.. 但時機係要等.. <br />\n總有一日做到"},{"pid":"068f2dde6adaf7756b08cdae0ae2eb927e99abfe","tid":1604422,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"總有一日會支爆<br />\n<br />\n乜都唔做等下先"},{"pid":"b0beff48700c164daba77d71a3864838128db513","tid":1604422,"uid":270196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068f2dde6adaf7756b08cdae0ae2eb927e99abfe","tid":1604422,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"總有一日會支爆<br />\n<br />\n乜都唔做等下先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:16:21.000Z","msg":"幫手推推行動po啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">[整合行動post] 9.30 罷唔罷？做乜好？ (求幫推置頂)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603201</a></span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b4ec60771547ccfc2dc88e176eda6349d9620c9","tid":1604422,"uid":249390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T03:22:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">十一賀佢老母！</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: orange;\"><s